{"tid":2352831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實中共用波台狗分化都幾高招","createTime":"2021-01-04T09:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T11:23:55.000Z","uid":367153,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df5084b164607596c88f6157c367b54897da642b","tid":2352831,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"中共嘅分化手段，相信大家都唔陌生<br />\n無非都係標籤+污名化<br />\n總之你講野唔啱就標籤你<br />\n香港人就標籤你港獨，台灣人就標籤你台獨<br />\n然後再污名化，話你搞事，暴動，分裂國家<br />\n<br />\n然後大家再睇下連登分化撚嘅手段<br />\n<br />\n<strong>標籤</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yfCaQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yfCaQp.jpg&h=a53c14f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總之睇開波就係波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>污名化</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rKzc4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rKzc4b.jpg&h=c7b20381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總之波台狗就係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見住連登日日屌波台狗，群眾鬥群眾，我哋五毛，呀唔係，要叫波台狗先啱，真係幾撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n波台撐奥燒？搞球迷connect集會？狗竇有光時口號？唔緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之睇波=波台狗=五毛"},{"pid":"058725e1ace768a3c95f8567ad841a1cf34e778c","tid":2352831,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:55:23.000Z","msg":"五毛唔敢入嚟駁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47ef15e521400dd603c2738995d948732d4886b","tid":2352831,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"駁唔到，密密留下負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25ab611d762a0f270ecbdc11ad49b8f22b394ba","tid":2352831,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:00:31.000Z","msg":"分化post ,拉 <br />\n<br />\n係三毛 ，PR 先會對號入座，求其出個pos